<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Password Reset OTP</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f6f8fb; color: #111827; margin: 0; padding: 24px; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .otp { font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 8px; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }
    .muted { color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer { margin-top: 28px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Password reset request</h2>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Use this 7-character OTP to reset your Proteccio CMS password:</p>
    <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
    <p class="muted">This OTP is valid for {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes. If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">&copy; {{year}} Proteccio Data</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
